node.text: Great times with everyone at @bootlegcanyonmtbpark last week! This particular trail always feels more like an enduro race on a downhill bike which is both fun and not fun in ways haha. Good to be back on track, can’t wait for the races to pick back up these next few months. Thanks to Mike and the staff for the hard work and fun weekend. 💪🏼👊🏼 @gopro #hero9black @intensecycles

node.text: Shooting with @clayporter for our upcoming series #TIMELESS. As you can see, it takes a long time to get up to speed fully on this road before we can film our shots. See if you can spot Clay filming on the side of the road near the end of the clip haha. Thankful to the mountain for the help and shuttles to pull this shoot off. @mammothmountain Definitely need to come back here with a special made bike, huge gearing, and a skin suit to reach maximum speeds. Haha We need sections like this in World Cup tracks. ✊🏼💨 #Iwannagofast @GoPro #Hero8black @intensecycles @intensefactoryracing @redbull @kendamtb @ethirteencomponents @trpcycling @ridefoxbike @alpinestars @bellbikehelmets @girocycling @smithoptics @htcomponents @odigrips @renthal_cycling @sdgcomponents @kogel_bearings @joesnoflats @motorex_bike @flattiredefend @rynopower @freshnlean @honda_powersports_us

node.text: Can’t believe it’s already been a year! It’s so much fun being married to you. Thanks babe for all your love and all you do. Can’t imagine things any different now, life is truly great with you by my side. Now get out of bed, I’m hungry, gonna make pancakes, and you’re taking forever. 😂🥞 I love you!!! 😘 @swannyberg

node.text: That new @thormxofficial race kit was lookin 🔥🔥 last weekend. We’ve been kinda flyin under the radar with this deal while we develop the new gear but man I’m stoked on this! Rode Thor gear as a kid racing Moto and it’s crazy to be the dude bringing them into the MTB scene now. Exciting things to come. 😎 #braaap

node.text: Wild day of racin! Rain set in about halfway through finals and made for a tough track. Felt I rode pretty solid for being in the latter half of the field but still got some work to do in these conditions. Up for the challenge, feelin positive and excited to get back to work and ready for the remainder of the season. So cool to have fans back at the races here too, thanks everyone for the noise and good vibes, missed this! 🤜🏼🤛🏼 #onward @intensecycles 📷 @aledilullophotography
